doctype html
html
  head
    block head
      meta(charset="utf-8")
      meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width")
      meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
      meta(name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting")
  body
    p Hello #{name},
    p Help us secure your #{brand} account by verifying your email address (#{email}). This lets you access all of #{brand}'s features.
    p Verify email address
    p #{action_url}
    hr
    p You’re receiving this email because you recently created a new #{brand} account or added a new email address. If this wasn’t you, please ignore this email.
    p If you run into problems, please contact support by visiting #{contacts_url}
    p Please do not reply to this email with your password. We will never ask for your password, and we strongly discourage you from sharing it with anyone.
